_sText: Simply unzip the "Hidden Map Pack.zip" file, unzip the "maps.zip" and "materials.zip" files and place both the "maps" and "materials" folder in your source cstrike folder (Default: C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\login name\counter-strike source\cstrike). You should get a warning saying that you already have a "maps" and "materials" folder and asking whether you want to overwrite or not, Say yes to all.
